{"tid":2098913,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭博社：華府曾討限制香港銀行買入美元的能力 又稱匯豐銀行或進首批制裁名單","createTime":"2020-07-08T00:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T06:00:59.000Z","uid":21470,"like":134,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"83cd50b2ec827f72d08cbddaf7008087cc6664d8","tid":2098913,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:20:38.000Z","msg":"彭博社：華府曾討論衝擊香港聯匯制度作為制裁措施<br />\n發佈時間 2020-07-08 08:01<br />\n<br />\n彭博通訊社報道，華府正討論在香港問題的制裁方案，其中國務卿蓬佩奧的顧問，曾經建議衝擊香港聯匯制度，包括限制香港銀行買入美元的能力，但蓬佩奧並無將有關方案提到白宮高層會議討論。報道指，有關建議受到<span style=\"color: gold;\">部份官員強烈反對</span>，擔心受傷害的是香港銀行及美國，而非中國。亦有人指，衝擊聯匯制度目前在一眾可能制裁方案中，排在較低位置，其他可能方案還包括消取港美引渡協定，以及終止與香港警隊的合作。 <br />\n<br />\n報道又指，華府正尋找懲罰本港銀行的方法，特別是匯豐銀行(<a href=\"http://00005.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00005.HK&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=a58b1563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00005.HK</a>)。 蓬佩奧曾經點名批評匯豐亞太區行政總裁王冬勝表態支持港區國安法是要表忠。美國國務院及財政部拒絕就報道評置。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2345922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2345922&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=cbcc6a40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2345922</a><br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧與方慧蘭通電話談及港區國安法等議題<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧與加拿大副總理方慧蘭通電話，慶祝《美墨加貿易協定》在本月1日正式生效。美國國務院聲明指，兩人同時討論有關北京制定港區國安法，以及兩名加拿大公民在中國被控間諜罪的事情。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，繼印度之後，華府亦正考慮禁用中國的社交應用程式，包括抖音海外版TikTok。加拿大公共安全部長布萊爾表示，暫時不會就下載使用TikTok發警告，但會與情報部門以及科技界合作，保障系統和公民安全。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2345910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2345910&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=592f1e75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2345910</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2345910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2345910&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=592f1e75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2345910</a>"},{"pid":"c54de5b005de6ab97d17d7a6287fc6e63ba797da","tid":2098913,"uid":278298,"like":66,"dislike":2,"score":64,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:25:01.000Z","msg":"「其他可能方案還包括消取港美引渡協定，以及終止與香港警隊的合作。」<br />\n<br />\n軟弱無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d055dcdd7acbd0c768437439d2dcfc297a674994","tid":2098913,"uid":1430,"like":51,"dislike":3,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:35:28.000Z","msg":"其他可能方案還包括消取港美引渡協定，以及終止與香港警隊的合作。 <br />\n<br />\n不痛不癢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係支那都唔驚啦"},{"pid":"bc907bc4dd67a8e234fc10a71ce4e38fd4056425","tid":2098913,"uid":124983,"like":10,"dislike":46,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:35:56.000Z","msg":"傾來傾去<br />\n有結論未大豆侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16e2b787074c5f2becab82248b0e32e933fa0ff","tid":2098913,"uid":37413,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:40:54.000Z","msg":"其他可能方案還包括消取港美引渡協定，以及終止與香港警隊的合作。 <br />\n<br />\n乜仲未終止㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fb427a861f5c23615ba28495182d793f39bb7f","tid":2098913,"uid":254594,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:41:23.000Z","msg":"其實唔多信會做<br />\n咁同以言入罪無乜分別<br />\n如果係凍結戶口呢d原因就可信d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb43885dfa8422feda134b3d6fd4c676ebfd27e5","tid":2098913,"uid":13343,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:41:53.000Z","msg":"次次都係吹淡風之後又變硬<br />\n唔好成日屌撚咗先<br />\n<b